{"tid":1086193,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[內蒙古遊記]我在草原馳騁的日子 (多圖+你問我盡答)","createTime":"2019-03-31T16:16:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T16:33:26.000Z","uid":241103,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6ec6f096f8346bf38acdc480e2bf27f704ce4898","tid":1086193,"uid":241103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T16:16:34.000Z","msg":"出發嗰朝，我地搭嘅係9點15分係深圳寶安機場飛海拉爾嘅機，晨咁早就係要係香港搭直通巴上深圳<br />\n<br />\n去到機場見有時間，同fd去買啲野食下先<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OossvFC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOossvFC.jpg&h=aec9d51e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qEojmNp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqEojmNp.jpg&h=f4d83f53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然話直飛，但係要係白塔機場落一落再上<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rC1QtsZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrC1QtsZ.jpg&h=9a2e7326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Si3fEzP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSi3fEzP.jpg&h=145c44ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到我地有個fd已經到咗同埋司機等緊我，但呢邊真心凍，9月已經冬天嘅溫度<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WHyrMgq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWHyrMgq.jpg&h=dce73667&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xXpbcVm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxXpbcVm.jpg&h=8385615f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n出發去酒店，途中風影<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AWVNvHt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAWVNvHt.jpg&h=1c8e95d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TyTZ6fy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTyTZ6fy.jpg&h=0a9fe20b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後去到酒店放低啲行李就出咗去食野，呢隻係我特登帶去嘅風箏<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b5c0QJr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb5c0QJr.jpg&h=a6e2a686&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一餐夠晒豐富，一人一鍋，啲牛羊肉真係食過返唔到轉頭<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/icLtZCc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FicLtZCc.jpg&h=a8d3273a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食完去咗散步，由於我地仲係市區，見到公園有唔少人，包括廣場舞大媽<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6YqBo4D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6YqBo4D.jpg&h=4798e9c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好平淡嘅第一日完"},{"pid":"94544f054487d7e186733f85a0c02abb4475b2cb","tid":1086193,"uid":152759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T16:33:26.000Z","msg":"打邊爐個張好似幾正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}